<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>Imgur Gallery</title><link>https://imgur.com</link><description>description</description><lastBuildDate>2022-02-01 03:29:14.612332</lastBuildDate><item><title>Labour problems</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wHoct4k</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/n9CNCU3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RPbA5Zs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/R7lmudm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>First visit to the hospital</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/z8xO9RY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Doctors did the test it was not water break</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Y2ruYKI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We are like ok no problem it’s understandable</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JpXsLIH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Contractions are starting to escalate</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pQIx6Jq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Second time going to the hospital</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9pitw8B.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Just to take off the edge</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aZlfXTD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We are 48 hours in, so we went for another check up for 3rd visit</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pLPOJrZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It also gave my wife just 30 minutes of sleep  but we still got sent to home</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zpumclh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Wife is in pain for next 12 hours</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UvQ7cAV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Doctor was very understandable</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/z6n3dCT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Finally</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xMPmWdI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I did not know that epidural is a complicated procedure and has to be done by anesthesiologist, and omg thank you for that my wife was able to take a solid 3 hours of sleep after 3 days  of pain</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bAx51G6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We are moving to OxyContin</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZNljQ4R.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>That was supposed to induce the full dilation it did not and we stack at 6CM</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tQxFbia.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Doctor’s only next choose is C-section</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LeUNMlD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yeah science baby</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tER1DZC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>That was quick I did not expected that</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/McnEQn6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KPQ5hkr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/V8bK78U.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My heart was racing on the way to see the baby ,it’s like you know it’s the love of your life and your just about to meet her</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6b5mE6K.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And here  she is</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UHfiJ9Q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Hi I’m Adeline</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pHN5lNn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is my dad</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Lq807yY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And this is me chilling in my moms hands</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wHoct4k</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[NikitaTokmakov]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Mad Dad</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/vOAiMNt</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/a5zxiGP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vOAiMNt</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ButtersTheCat]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Seems pretty simple to me</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wTFAl4J</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LJ66RgS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wTFAl4J</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CapCap]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Same planet, different destinies</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/JnWdjOw</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/59sMe5x.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>1.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JQaWr48.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>2.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/z5YDwoB.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>3.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JqSE6mZ.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>4.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vU1luq6.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>5.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rkZn1oE.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>6.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cVgwVsd.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>7.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OlYSVV9.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>8.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HMAcuH0.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>9.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jVJJ7IY.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>The photo on the left, entitled "The Struggling Girl" was taken by Kevin Carter. He won a pulitzer prize for this photo, depicting a starving child crawling towards a food centre a half mile away. He faced heavy criticism for not helping the child and took his own life 4 months after receiving the award. The child survived. The artist of this photo montage is Ugur Gallenkus, a Turkish graphic designer.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JnWdjOw</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[arewenotkingsandqueenstogether]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Remembering the good old Covid daya</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/TCiooxq</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qjAC64Y.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/TCiooxq</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ninety2]]></