lenadirscherl.com
lenadirscherl.tumblr.com
https://www.instagram.com/bopolena/

The title of the post is taken from all airlines in the world. Ever notice how few things we agree on as one human race?  This is one of few. Your chance of taking care of someone else is reduced or eliminated unless you take care of you first. 

You can argue, make scenarios, deny the case studies ... but you're not going to change the facts of human psychology. It doesn't mean being selfish and ignoring others. Just a question of an order of sequence. Steps.

----------------------------------------
Today's Internet message: 
Men - Stop worrying every minute about how you look compared to some perfect societal image. 

You're okay right now! If you want to improve, set your own reasonable goals based on what YOU want. Set goals healthwise, your own appearance standards and a partner who respects you!!

Often it's best to get help if you're always looking for a diet or workout to "make you feel better" about yourself. It's worse if someone in a relationship of any kind is trying to make you fit an image THEY have of what you should be. 

I encourage you to seek a professional immediately. Self diagnosis is generally not a good thing. I tried it for 10+ years. Didn't work.

This website can help you find someone near you to talk diagnoses:
https://www.psychologytoday.com/
[ I have zero association with psychologytoday or any other company or advertising scheme. I'm a semi-retired engineering manager. Just an Imgurian like you. ]

Think of it like going to Urgent Care or Emergency Room if you have a serious cut or cough. A professional will tell you next steps - do not self diagnose.

If you have a more serious mental health issue, call 911 (US) or message the people at places in this post: https://imgur.com/gallery/cAppClq</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ojyO4r3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[epicurusaquinas]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Things To Think About</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/WATAufS</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YGlIOKW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/WATAufS</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>You lookin' at me?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/GMFXeGI</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sMVwkKP.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My ego would have got in the way when I was younger, but I like this!

